products.title: Impressions Grained Cream Faux Wood
products.description: The impressions fauxwood range is stylish and sumptuous. This solid cream wooden blind is a great way to add more character to your space. Slats of the blind come grained which adds depth and texture to the finished look. At swift direct blinds, quality is important to us, not only does this faux wooden blinds come with a fabulous five year guarantee, but customer-first service and industry-leading delivery times.
